      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>Founded in 2018, Shopzilla began as a simple idea: to create an online shopping platform that truly puts customers first. Our founders, frustrated with complicated checkout processes and poor customer service elsewhere, set out to build something better.</p>
      <p>What started as a small team of five has grown into a thriving company serving over one million customers worldwide. We've maintained our core values of quality, transparency, and exceptional customer service throughout our journey.</p>
      <p>Today, we're proud to offer thousands of carefully curated products from trusted brands and emerging innovators. Our commitment to sustainability, innovation, and customer satisfaction drives everything we do.</p>
    </div>
